@{
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Lỗi — TechZone</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@400;600;700;900&family=Nunito:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css">
    <style>
        body { background: var(--black); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; margin: 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="denied-wrap">
        <div class="denied-card">
            <div class="denied-icon">⚠️</div>
            <div class="denied-title">Đã xảy ra lỗi</div>
            <div class="denied-sub">
                Rất tiếc, đã có lỗi xảy ra trong quá trình xử lý yêu cầu của bạn.<br>
                Vui lòng thử lại hoặc quay về trang chủ.
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;">
                <a href="~/"
                   style="display:block;padding:13px;text-align:center;background:var(--blue);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:8px;font-family:var(--font-head);font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;">
                    ← Quay về trang chủ
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
